data.description: Step into perfection with this well-maintained home showing pride of ownership, promising a haven of comfort and style. A must-see Ranch style home sits on an oversized corner lot. The backyard oasis is an entertainers dream with a blend of comfort and space where there's endless possibilities meet tranquility. The heart of the home is in the spacious kitchen where creativity meets functionality with the combined dining area creating the perfect harmony for shared moments. This  3 bedroom 1 bath home, includes a basement with freedom of an open room a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch.
